_sText:
Hi there
I've quickly made a kind of aim_map, inspirate from de_dust2 gameplay. The principe is quite simple: no bombs, no hostages and a different gun at each round for the whole players (choice between deagle, shotgun, m4, and awp).
It's not a realistic map, so i decide to use Tags in a different way.
As I said, it is done rather quickly, therefore it is not very detailed nor very complicated, the ambition is also rather simple: funny games, and it is all.
